    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "CATHAY PACIFIC AIRWAYS LTD.\nSwire House, 8 Spring St., Sydney, Australia.\nVR-HDB - DC3\nFarewell Flight\nAUSTRALIA 1 9 SEP 1983\n1 1 7 SEP 1983\n110\nstralia\nAIR MAIL\n27c\nQID\nCATHAY PACIFIC AIRWAYS LTD.\nPublic Relations Department\nG.P.O. Box 1\nHong Kong\n18th-23rd September, 1983\nSydney Cairns-Wewak-Davao-Manila-HongKong\nCATHAY PACIFIC\nThe Swire Group BR",
      "VR-HDB is Cathay Pacific Airways first aircraft and was in service with the airline from its founding in 1946 until 1953.\nThis farewell flight is undertaken prior to the DC3 being presented to the Hong Kong Museum of Science and Technology.\n2007,011.418"
